OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will become increasingly
OL,6,Fcloudy in the morning with rain for a
OL,7,Ftime. Turning mostly dry and somewhat
OL,8,Fbrighter in the afternoon, but the odd
OL,9,Fshower possible. Warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some brightness to
OL,12,Fstart but rain spreading north in the
OL,13,Fevening. This clearing shortly after
OL,14,Fmidnight to leave a dry night with
OL,15,Fsome clear spells developing.
OL,16,
OL,17,CFriday:FWarm again on Friday. Dry
OL,18,Fthrough much of the day with bright or
OL,19,Fsunny spells. The odd shower possible
OL,20,Fin the afternoon ahead of some rain in
OL,21,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
