OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FWarm
OL,6,Fover the weekend with some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells, chance of some rain
OL,8,Flater on Sunday. A touch cooler Monday
OL,9,Fbut still dry with bright spells.
